    "description": "Comprehensive API test collection for Restful-Booker (https://restful-booker.herokuapp.com).\n\nCovers: Health check, Auth token creation, full Booking CRUD (GET all, GET by ID, POST create, PUT update, PATCH partial update, DELETE), and negative test scenarios for each endpoint.\n\nAuthor: Daniel Oyebode — Senior QA Automation Engineer | ISTQB Certified\nGitHub: https://github.com/danieloyebode/postman-restfulbooker-api",
